Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 那把短劍是誰的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose dagger was it, Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥 他被索隆的仆從殺害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother. He was killed by servants of Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔茍斯戰敗后 你們稱之為索隆的那一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After Morgoth's defeat, the one you call Sauron,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖打造一種力量 并非來源于肉體 而是讓肉體受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he sought to craft a power not of the flesh, but over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I killed Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á kuita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 快回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Dilly, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但盡管我們竭盡全力 枯萎還是加速了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But despite our every effort, our decline has only quickened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個秘銀…是我們唯一的救贖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This mithril... It is our only salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事物都無法削弱它的光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing diminishes its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都林國王… -夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-King Durin... -Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會拿矮人們的生命冒險 去幫助精靈逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not risk Dwarven lives to help the Elves cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等待你的將是黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All that awaits you there is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找掩護\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿達爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar! Adar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開這片大陸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us put this land behind our sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-與你并肩作戰 我感覺… -我也感覺到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fighting at your side, I felt... -I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傷口需要精靈族的藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wound needs Elvish medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜國王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-警告他將要發生的事情 -獨自前往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Warn him what's comin'. -Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會獨行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大綠林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not a peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們前來為您效勞 索隆大君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We come to serve you, Lord Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指環王：力量之戒\N第一季第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾加拉德明天到達\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gil-galad arrives tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我們匯報 能夠拯救所有精靈王國的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}expecting to be presented with a means of saving all Elvendom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們卻一籌莫展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有某種方式…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only there was some way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠事半功倍就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of doing more with less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽剛誕生的時候 還沒有我的巴掌大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Sun itself began as something no bigger than the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的力量 怎么能與太陽的創造者相提并論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how could we possibly match the powers that wrought the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒時間了 凱勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're out of time, Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須告知至高王我們失敗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must inform the High King of our failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來精靈必須 做好準備 永久放棄這片海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Elves must prepare to abandon these shores. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六天前 他被敵人的長矛刺中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Enemy lance. Six days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬不停蹄地趕了過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We rode without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能救救他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒來吧…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á tul? koivienna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方大地的國王  你怎么會和他有交集呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}King of the Southlands? How is it your path crossed with his?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么會在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么會在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我們有很多事情要談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. We have much to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初就不應該讓你上那艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have set you on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本應該相信你的 這種錯誤我以后不會再犯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have trusted you. It is a mistake I will not make again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從那艘船上跳下來…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I leapt from that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我深知自己還不配重返維林諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I believed in my heart I was not yet worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道 不知何故 自己在這里的任務還沒有完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew that, somehow, my task here was not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我浮出水面時 我能做的只有拼命游泳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when I surfaced, all I could do was swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并祈禱自己做了明智之選\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and pray I had chosen wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初游過那片苦海…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not cross that bitter ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是為了現在功敗垂成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only to drown now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不能讓你失敗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nor will I let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我們唯一能做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使勁地游\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在那兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在那兒 出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's there? Reveal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾在這里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Galadriel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在休息嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't you be resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里曾是凱勒布林博的工作間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was the workshop of Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位凱勒布林博嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Celebrimbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會在這里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's not here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…其實 他就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... As a matter of fact, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒布林博…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我師從的那位大師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The master I apprenticed to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前經常說起你無與倫比的手藝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}used to speak of the wonders of your craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未曾想過自己能有機會親眼所見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never dreamed that I'd ever get the chance to see them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是鐵匠嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…我跟您可沒法相提并論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... Nothing like your artistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些寶石 我從未見過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These gemstones, I've never seen anything like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用它們做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you plan to use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費艾諾的珠寶工藝 成功地捕捉到了維林諾的圣光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F?anor's jewelcraft managed to capture the essence of Valinor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能在中洲如法炮制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped to do the same for Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種礦石很奇特 它是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a peculiar ore. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請還給我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有試過將它 和其他礦石結合 更好地發揮潛能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you tried combining it with other ores? To better stretch it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種礦石不適合這樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wouldn't be suitable for this ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-為什么不行  -因為所需數量龐大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why not? -Because in the amounts we need,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會大幅稀釋其獨一無二的品質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would too greatly dilute its unique qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的問題可能會有點蠢 請見諒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, but, uh, at the risk of sounding a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰當的合金組合 難道不是能強化這些品質嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}couldn't the right alloy also amplify those qualities?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Amplify?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我練手藝的地方 貴重金屬簡直是鳳毛麟角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where I came up, precious metals were scarce as hens' teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們學會了 將各種金屬結合 從而揚長避短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-So we learnt to combine them to harness strengths and hide flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾見過在鐵中 添加微量的鎳 使刀鋒更輕 更堅固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen a trace of nickel added to iron to make a blade lighter and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這種礦石 難道沒有合金能強化它的品質嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might there not be some alloy to amplify the qualities of your ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個建議有點意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that is... an intriguing suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱之為…天賦吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call it... a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 他將踏上 那條所有人都會踏上的歸途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, he will travel that road which makes an end of every man who walks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口將會一片悲慟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Black flags will fill our harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有責任為他建造一座墳墓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be our duty to forge for him a tomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用石頭賦予他不朽之身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}granting him the immortality in stone that no man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不朽 任何人 任何國王都無法獲得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not even a king, can attain in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經召集了努門諾爾 各地的繪圖員前來描繪國王的容貌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Draftsmen from across Númenor have been summoned to capture his visage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓他們給出一個圖樣方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they can propose a design.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在所有的學徒之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of all the apprentices,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要提出一項圖樣方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have been chosen to propose one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接下來的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the coming days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們每個人 都將獲準與國王相處一小時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}each of you will be granted one hour with the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好利用這段時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道黑夜里你一直在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what you have been doing in the dark of night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你以為大家都睡著了 -對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-when you thought all eyes were asleep. -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的侍女馬上就會回來 國王大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your handmaid will be back in a moment, my king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么還有時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有時間干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間警告你 年輕的彌瑞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To warn you, young Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您搞錯了 我不是… -還不是女王嗎 沒關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You're mistaken. I'm not... -Queen yet? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你會成為女王的 所以聽好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you will be. So know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能盡快恢復 我們與精靈族往日的交好與聯盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if the old ways of our people are not soon restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的島嶼將會陷落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our island will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是國王 救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the king! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧 你必須得走上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. You must go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但別像我那樣找尋了太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't do as I did. I looked for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我已分不清現在與過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, I cannot separate what is from what was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也分不清過去與未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what was from what will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個中洲 仰賴一物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One object. For all Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 我知道這聽起來很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it sounds strange, High King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以肯定 我們窮盡了所有可能的解決方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But surely, we should exhaust every possible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么樣的物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Precisely what manner of object?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會比之前想象的要小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be smaller than previously imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以隨身攜帶的物品…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something that could be carried...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一把權杖 -一把劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A scepter perhaps. -A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是…一頂王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or perhaps... A crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么是王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why a crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環形會是理想之選\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A circular form will be ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完整的環狀物中 光線能在弧形里折射回自身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allowing the light to arc back upon itself in one unbroken round,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打造出一種近乎無限的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}building to a power that is all but unbounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你要把這所有力量 都集中在一個精靈的頭頂之上嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you would place all that power upon the brow of one being?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是隨便哪個精靈 而是您啊至高王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not just any one being, High King. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些悄聲暗示危險得很…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perilous are these whisperings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的時候 危險的那條道路才是唯一的出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes the perilous path is the only path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我也不會站在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be standing here otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來就不應該在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not be standing here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 我們只求給夠時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, we ask only for the time needed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集精靈巧匠 測試凱勒布林博的理論…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to gather the Elven-smiths and test Celebrimbor's theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的時間不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our time runs short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒錯 所以… -時間比你們了解的還要緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yes, that is why... -Shorter than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從南方大地的火山爆發后 大樹的枝葉就開始瘋狂掉落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since the mountain of fire's eruption, the Great Tree is all but bleeding leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 最后一片樹葉也將凋落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, the last will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我們的人民 離開這片海岸 否則我們也將衰亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And unless our people leave these shores, so shall we.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中洲沒有哪個精靈 比我更迫切想要找出解決方案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no Elf in Middle-earth who wanted a solution more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果這真能拯救我們 恐怕還得再快一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if this was to be our salvation, I'm afraid we needed it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來差點就完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I almost had it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過因為 和那個來自南方大地的人說話…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was only in speaking with the Southlander that I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個下等人 這個主意是他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The low man? This idea was his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是他的建議 才讓我想出了這個解決方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His suggestions were but the key that unlocked the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼看著就要打造出一股新的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are on the cusp of crafting a new kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物理力量 而是精神力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not of strength, but of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非來源于肉體 而是讓肉體受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not of the flesh, but over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可見世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a power of the Unseen World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 領主凱勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry, Lord Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此命令你解散這座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are hereby commanded to disband the city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并立即返回林頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and return to Lindon immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們大家都是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話 “控制肉體的力量”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those words, "a power over flesh."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪里聽到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在和巧匠們商議 我覺得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was conferring with my smiths. I think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那句是我的原話 -哈爾布蘭德剛才和你在一起嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I believe those are my words. -Was Halbrand with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要嗎 反正已經結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it matter? It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉… -給我三個月時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I am sorry... -Grant me three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我三個月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am owed that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不欠你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are owed nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別為了補償我而答應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then do it not out of recompense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我求您的份上 答應我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it because I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是虛假的希望 埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a fool's hope, Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已 再無更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Merely that. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“希望從來都不是 微不足道的 即便希望很渺茫”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Hope is never mere. Not even when it is meager."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你已經忘了自己的忠告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or have you forgotten your own counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找皇室血脈的記錄 要找出與南方大地有關的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need royal lineages, bloodlines. Anything you can find on the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對凡人王國的記錄有限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our records are limited concerning the mortal kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些信息我得去地下墓穴里找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have to scour the catacombs for that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-躲起來 -三個星期…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come. -Three weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這工作耗時三個世紀 卻只給我三個星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three weeks for a labor that could take three centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊迫的時間就是發明的動力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Constraint can be the very progenitor of invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 別對任何人提起此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Speak of this to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒布林博會找到辦法的 我很確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor will find a way. I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然之間你們倆彼此這么熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of a sudden, the two of you seem quite familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是盡己所能 提供一些微不足道的幫助而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just offering whatever humble aid I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我還是不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To tell you the truth, I can still hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的人居然能在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone like me, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與埃瑞吉安的精靈巧匠共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working with the Elven-smiths of Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝我把你帶來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For bringing you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也救過我 我們互不相欠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you saved mine. Our scales are balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你為我做的遠不止這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you've done far more than that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就放棄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd all but given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你選擇了相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you, you believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我身上看到了力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saw strength in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我拔高到了 其他人無法幫我實現的高度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You pushed me to heights that no one else could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我永遠不會忘卻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會確保其他人也永遠銘記\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll see to it that no one else does either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 別害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not be afraid, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的力量越覺醒 迷霧就會越弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The more your powers awaken, the more the veil will weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷霧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些打敗您的人 在您的腦海中設下的障礙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one placed upon your mind by those who cast you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們前來就是為了歡迎您的回歸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we have come here to welcome you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將您接回我們的領土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To bring you to our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的領土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您其實已經知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做隱士之帽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is called the Hermit's Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在一個地方能看到這個星座圖案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A pattern visible in but one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠的東方 那里的星座圖案很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far to the east, where the stars are strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯恩之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lands of Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-魯恩… -沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Rh?n... -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的真實身份 最終將在那里為眾人所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you will be known at last, for who you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從星空墜入凡間 但卻比星星更加偉大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fell from the stars, yet you are greater than they.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為火會服從您的意志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For fire obeys your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您倒在凡塵之下 而凡塵卻懼怕于您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fell below the dust, yet dust fears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為您若發怒 凡塵皆顫抖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For it trembles when you are wroth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風和水 冷與熱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The winds and waters, the heat and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.37,0:22:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您將在魯恩學會控制所有這些力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Rh?n, you shall learn to command them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個行走或爬行的生物 都將成為您的奴隸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every being that walks or crawls shall be your slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因為您是索隆大君 -因為您是索隆大君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you are Lord Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:22:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假以時日 他將學會控制自己的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In time, he will learn to control his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在 暫時先把他綁起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now, bind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們確實有出餿主意的“優良”傳統 但這回恐怕是最餿的一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, in the grand tradition of bad ideas, this might well be the worst yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你有更好的想法嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, have you got a better notion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個居住者不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Third one's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd the third one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個總比三個強 現在就是我們的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better two than three. Now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蘭地足 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.83,0:25:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 冷靜下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Master, calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.70,0:26:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞 我們走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nori. Nori, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.16,0:27:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他睜開眼看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make him see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你 求你了 拿著吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need you. Please, just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.58,0:28:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我遠點 否則我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from me. Or I wi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.95,0:28:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再次傷害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will hurt you. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.75,0:28:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 他們對你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? What have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.91,0:28:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們向我展示了我的真實身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They showed me what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份只有你自己才能決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only you can show what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.08,0:29:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行為決定了你的善惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You choose by what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來幫忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.66,0:29:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.91,0:29:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛閉上 只會疼一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close your eyes. -It'll only hurt but a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.41,0:29:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.95,0:30:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們從黑影中來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From shadow you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.83,0:30:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你們滾回黑影中去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To shadow I bid you return!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.12,0:30:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他不是索隆 -他是另外一個 是那個伊斯塔爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He is not Sauron. -He is the other. The Istar. He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.04,0:31:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.29,0:31:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動 我們會想辦法把你帶回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold still. We'll find a way to carry you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.79,0:31:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 好姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, good lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我就要偏離軌道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I'm about to go a' wandering off-trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.70,0:31:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布羅斯先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Burrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 普羅德菲洛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, Proudfellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.29,0:31:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人肯定會在那邊等著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The missus will be waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.62,0:31:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意 我現在只想坐一會兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you don't mind, I'd just like to sit a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著看太陽升起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watch the Sun come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.45,0:33:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.16,0:33:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四 五 六\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-four, five, six,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.29,0:33:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七 八…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.16,0:33:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是九步…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.70,0:33:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到主桿一共九級臺階\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stairs to main-post.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您做得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.33,0:33:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 你敢再這樣憐憫我 我就降你的職\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patronize me like that again, Captain, I'll have your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.87,0:33:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.54,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我護著你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.62,0:33:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰來護著你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who has you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.33,0:34:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑒于你的喪子之痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Given your loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.79,0:34:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去后 如果你想請辭 我非常理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would understand it if upon our return, you wish to take a leave of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有一次問我 為什么要把加拉德瑞爾從海里救出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You once asked me why I pulled Galadriel from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.25,0:34:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自稱當時別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I claimed to have had little choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.87,0:34:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實是 我本可以把她留在海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the truth is, I could have left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本可以拒絕隨她到中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could've refused to follow her to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.58,0:34:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者阻止我兒子去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or stopped my son from doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在每一個轉折點 我都做出了當下的選擇 因為…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet at every turn, I made the choices I did because...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 埃蘭迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, Elendil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.45,0:34:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為“埃蘭迪爾” 不光意味著“愛星星的人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because "Elendil" does not merely mean "one who loves the stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是沒想到會導致現在這種結局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just never imagined it would lead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親曾經告訴我 忠貞派的處事方式就是要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father once told me that the way of The Faithful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.16,0:35:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心實意付出代價…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is committing to pay the price...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便還不知道代價會是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if the cost cannot be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.58,0:35:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要相信 付出的代價終將會是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And trusting that, in the end, it will be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.79,0:35:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候代價會很高昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes the cost is dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.75,0:35:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們別無選擇 只能繼續履職盡責\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have little choice then but to keep serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.25,0:35:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我敢說 我會讓結局對得起這份代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I, for one, will see to it that we make the end worth the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.79,0:35:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come what may?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.41,0:35:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come what may.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 能看見努門諾爾了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Captain. Númenor is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.79,0:36:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.04,0:36:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃蘭迪爾 怎么了 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil, what is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.70,0:36:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.29,0:37:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.58,0:37:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀太孤傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mithril is proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.75,0:37:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它拒絕與次等礦石結合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It refuses every effort to bond it with lesser ores.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.83,0:38:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汲取物質世界和不可見世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tapping into the powers of the Seen and Unseen World
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.58,0:38:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎弱化了兩者之間的界限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seemed to soften the boundaries between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.41,0:38:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本講不通啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.66,0:38:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們施加的壓力 大到能讓天地都融為一體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We used enough pressure to fuse the heavens with earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.45,0:38:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這次本來應該行啊  -要有耐心 這是一個過程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It should have held this time! -Patience. This is a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.79,0:38:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非每次努力 都是朝著進步的方向 這需要時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not every step we take will be forward. It may take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-時間 我們沒有時間 -時間…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Time? We don't... We don't have time. -Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不今天就到這里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps that is enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們把自己逼得太緊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we've been pushing ourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.12,0:38:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我們把自己逼得太緊了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Pushing ourselves too hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.29,0:38:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如說這就是問題所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing that's the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.54,0:38:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如說是我們用力過猛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing we've been using too much force?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.37,0:38:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.50,0:38:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是不應該強迫金屬的結合…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning that the metals shouldn't be forced to join...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.75,0:38:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是應該將彼此吸引 誘導到一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But more drawn or coaxed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.75,0:38:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣 那我們一直在朝反方向努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if that's true, we've been... we've been doing it all inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.04,0:38:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把它拆開 我們重新開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quickly. Dismantle this. We start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.62,0:39:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.95,0:39:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到方法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道以前怎么沒發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how we missed it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的力量過于強大 單個物體無法承受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's too much power for one object.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.29,0:39:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要兩個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.66,0:39:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要做兩個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're making two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.95,0:39:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-兩個王冠  -不完全是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Two crowns? -Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.62,0:39:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得做成稍微…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll need to be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.66,0:39:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小一點的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.54,0:39:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你自己看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.75,0:39:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先告訴我你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not until you tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.87,0:39:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說你真正的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.54,0:40:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 恐怕我聽不…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, I'm afraid I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.87,0:40:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有南方大地的國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no King of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.00,0:40:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條血脈早就斷掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The line was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.50,0:40:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上的徽章 它最后的主人 早在一千多年前就去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last man to bear your crest died over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.29,0:40:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他沒有繼承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had no heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你 我是在死人身上找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I found it on a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.66,0:40:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.58,0:40:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 在木筏上 你救了我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, on the raft, you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在木筏上 是你救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the raft, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.50,0:40:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說服了彌瑞爾出兵拯救中洲的人類\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You convinced Míriel to save the Men of Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.41,0:40:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說服了她 我當時可是想留在努門諾爾的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You convinced her. I wanted to remain in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與我并肩作戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fought beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.75,0:40:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗擊你的敵人 以及我的敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Against your enemy. And mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.87,0:41:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打創始之初 我就已經醒來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been awake since before the breaking of the first silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.58,0:41:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…我有很多個名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that time... I have had many names.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.33,0:41:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒站穩當吧 妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lose your footing again, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.79,0:41:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是摔了一下而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was just a little tumble, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.00,0:41:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your feet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.16,0:42:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出我的大腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.41,0:42:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.20,0:42:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.41,0:42:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的舊短劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My old dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.62,0:42:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間你一直好好保管著它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've kept it safe all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.83,0:42:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你苦苦戰斗了這么多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have fought so hard. For so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.70,0:42:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去完成我的未竟之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To complete the task that I could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.37,0:42:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是獵殺索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your task was hunting Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.20,0:42:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務是確保和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My task was to ensure peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.91,0:42:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我了解到 索隆的任務也是確保和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I learned that was Sauron's task as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.16,0:43:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.87,0:43:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.16,0:43:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為索隆 你和無數精靈一起犧牲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Along with countless others, because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.83,0:43:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.75,0:43:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他尋求力量并不是為了摧毀中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was seeking a power not to destroy Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.00,0:43:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是將其治愈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的精靈同胞們 正在力求做到的那樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as your fellow Elves are seeking to do this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.41,0:43:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必對他們撒謊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You needn't lie to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.37,0:43:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只消讓工作繼續進行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Simply let the work proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.66,0:43:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得就在這棵樹下 我對你耳語的那番話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember what I whispered to you under this very tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.87,0:43:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再觸碰一次黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Touch the darkness once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥死了 全都是因為你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother is dead. Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.58,0:44:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 你為什么要說這種話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.20,0:44:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么要說這樣的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.25,0:44:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.29,0:44:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 回到我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.83,0:44:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.16,0:44:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.87,0:44:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.79,0:44:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔茍斯的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a friend of Morgoth's.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.50,0:44:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年魔茍斯被打敗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When Morgoth was defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.62,0:45:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一個攥緊的大拳頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was as if a great, clenched fist
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.79,0:45:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的脖子上松開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}had released its grasp from my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.04,0:45:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一個日出的寂靜之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the stillness of that first sunrise,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.75,0:45:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終于又感受到了獨一之神的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at last, I felt the light of The One again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.62,0:45:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道如果我想得到寬恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I knew if ever I was to be forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.20,0:45:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須治愈 我曾助紂為虐破壞掉的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I had to heal everything that I had helped ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.79,0:45:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何補贖都無法抹去你犯下的惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No penance could ever erase the evil you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.54,0:45:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你根本不是這樣想的 -我的想法用不著你說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-That is not what you believe. -Do not tell me what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.83,0:45:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你告訴我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.50,0:45:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們勝利之后 你說我不必再糾結以前做過的任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After our victory, you said that whatever I'd done before I could be free of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.45,0:45:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是你騙我在先 -我告訴了你真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You deceived me. -I told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你我做過惡 是你不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you that I had done evil, and you did not care.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.58,0:45:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你知道 跟我們的未來相比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you knew that our past meant nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.04,0:45:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的過去毫無意義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}weighed against our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有這樣的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no such future.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.91,0:45:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.29,0:46:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都用懷疑的眼光看待你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All others look on you with doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有我能看到你的偉大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I alone can see your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.45,0:46:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能看到你的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I alone can see your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.50,0:46:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會讓我變成暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would make me a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.00,0:46:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你成為女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would make you a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.04,0:46:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像大海和太陽一樣美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fair as the sea and the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.87,0:46:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比大地的根基還要堅固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stronger than the foundations of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.25,0:46:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你 國王大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you. My king.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.70,0:46:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗魔君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.87,0:46:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.95,0:46:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在我身邊 就不會是黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with you at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.95,0:47:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經告訴我 命運有意把我們安排在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me once, that we were brought together for a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.29,0:47:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.54,0:47:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贈我以光芒 我賜你以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bind me to the light. And I bind you to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以一起拯救中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together, we can save this Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.04,0:47:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是統治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.66,0:47:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這二者沒什么區別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.45,0:47:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什么… 我永遠不會站在你那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that is why... I will never be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.58,0:47:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.20,0:47:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我 你們精靈將會衰落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without me, your people will fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.37,0:47:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影將會蔓延 加重 直至籠罩整個世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the shadow will spread and darken to cover all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.66,0:47:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你需要我 -我當初就應該把你丟在海上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You need me. -I should have left you on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.33,0:47:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時在海里 就是因為精靈們把你趕了出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A sea you were on because the Elves cast you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.87,0:47:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把你趕走 就因為你乞求他們給你幾個士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They cast you out for deigning to beg them for a few petty soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.37,0:47:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你告訴他們 你是我的盟友時 他們會怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will they do when you tell them that you were my ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.95,0:48:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你告訴他們是你救活了索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you tell them that Sauron lives because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.62,0:48:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you will die because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.66,0:48:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.16,0:48:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deceiver!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.04,0:48:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 住手  埃爾隆德 是埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Galadriel, stop! Elrond. It's Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.45,0:48:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明給我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.75,0:49:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第一次見面是在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did we first meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.70,0:49:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海濱 當時我剛成為孤兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seaside. When I was first orphaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.79,0:49:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獨自一人 是個年幼的 半精靈男孩 舉目無親 也沒有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was alone. A young, half-elven boy, without friend or kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.62,0:49:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給了我水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave me water.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.66,0:49:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.75,0:49:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}á cuith tess?, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.29,0:49:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱勒布林博在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.29,0:49:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作間 他馬上就要完工了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Workshop. He'll almost be finished by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.75,0:49:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.08,0:49:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel! Galadriel! What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.54,0:49:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.08,0:49:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.79,0:49:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 你渾身濕透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. You're as wet as a river rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.50,0:49:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.66,0:49:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛把她 從格藍都因河中拖了出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I pulled her from the waters of Glanduin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:49:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格藍都因河 怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Glanduin? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.70,0:50:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.25,0:50:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Halbrand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.20,0:50:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他走了 我懷疑他不會回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is gone. And I doubt he will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.04,0:50:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再回來 誰都不準再與他聯絡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And should he ever, none of us are to treat with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.33,0:50:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條溪流旁發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened by that stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.50,0:50:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前跟我說你犯過一個錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You spoke to me once of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.79,0:50:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不會再犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One you said you would not make again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.12,0:50:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你讓我這個承諾很難兌現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're making that promise very difficult to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.83,0:50:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是容易辦到的話 也就不需要信任了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were it easy, it would not require trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.37,0:50:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們繼續嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, do we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.37,0:50:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.95,0:50:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須做三個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must make three.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.04,0:50:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個 為什么要三個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three? Why three?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.79,0:50:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單個容易墮落 成雙總會分裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One will always corrupt. Two will divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.75,0:50:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而三個 就有了平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But with three, there is balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.37,0:51:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天鍛造的力量必須只屬于精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The powers we forge today must be for the Elves alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.41,0:51:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得被他人觸及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Untouched by other hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.66,0:51:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 我已經確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, I have determined that the purity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.62,0:51:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合金中次要礦石的純度至關重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the lesser ores in the alloy is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.25,0:51:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要最精純的金銀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need gold and silver of the most exquisite quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.79,0:51:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要維林諾的金銀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need gold and silver from Valinor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.45,0:51:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的創造需要…犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True creation requires... sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.08,0:51:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得其他什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember anything more yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.29,0:51:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一些碎片的印象了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fragments. Impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.33,0:52:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想起來的越來越多 但為了找到 余下的記憶 我必須前往魯恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More has come. But to discover the rest, I know I must go to Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.62,0:52:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把你的名字都搞錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were wrong about your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.87,0:52:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們把地名 也弄錯了呢 或者撒謊了 或者…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if they're wrong about that, too? Or lying, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.45,0:52:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他們說的是真的 但我無法解釋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What they said, I knew to be true with a... a certainty that I can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.29,0:52:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.33,0:52:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們稱呼你為“伊斯塔爾”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They called you something else. "Istar."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.08,0:52:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的種族嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that your kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.54,0:52:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“伊斯塔爾”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Istar?"
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.08,0:52:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們的語言中 意思是“智者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In your tongue, that means "wise one."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.41,0:52:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.45,0:52:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“巫師”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Wizard."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.41,0:52:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不和我們一起走嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're really not coming with us, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.62,0:53:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時 我們的前路 早已被更強大的力量所安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Betimes, our paths are laid before us by powers greater than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.75,0:53:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時 我們的任務就是要百折不撓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In those moments, it's our task to make our feet go
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.70,0:53:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅決踏上心里所忌憚的那條道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where our hearts wish not to tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.04,0:53:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論沿途有什么危險在等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the perils awaiting us on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.87,0:53:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來有點像冒險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Sounds a bit like an adventure. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.58,0:53:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一個人而言 只是旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alone, it's just a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.58,0:53:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一群人而言 才是冒險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now adventures, they must be shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.70,0:53:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我冒過的險 比任何毛腳族能想到的還要多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think I've had about as much adventure as any Harfoot could ever hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.75,0:53:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里寫道 如果往北走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Says here, if we go north-ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.16,0:53:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上我們會有三十天都很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have thirty days of clear trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.79,0:53:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是新鮮草地 沒有食人妖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All fresh grass and no trolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.95,0:54:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 看起來好像都是下坡… -你拿倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, hey, hey! -All downhill, look like... -You're holding it upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.70,0:54:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瑪爾娃 我們要連續數周爬坡過坎披荊斬棘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Malva. Nothing but steep slopes and brickle-brambles for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.58,0:54:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這么聰明 怎么不去探路呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if you're so quick and wise, why don't you do the trail-finding?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.08,0:54:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加留意小孩和掉隊者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch out for little ones and stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.25,0:54:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人偏離路線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody goes off-trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.91,0:54:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有人獨自前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nobody walks alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.83,0:54:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是從薩道克的嘴里 說出來更好聽一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounded better when Sadoc said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.12,0:54:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望那個糟老頭子還和我們在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wish the old goat were still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.70,0:54:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他與我們同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.41,0:54:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.62,0:54:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在有更重要的事情要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a part of something bigger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.20,0:55:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He needs ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.58,0:55:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你屬于外面的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you belong out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.41,0:55:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good-bye, Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.87,0:55:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再見… -要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Good-bye... -Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.62,0:55:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.95,0:55:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你帶燈了嗎  -當然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Did you pack your lantern? -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.29,0:55:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.41,0:55:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧…再見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.87,0:55:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瑞…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.45,0:55:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這是給那個大家伙吃的蝸牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Here's snails for the big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.87,0:55:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道他胃口有多大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know how hungry he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.83,0:56:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多帶一條毯子 以防感冒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an extra blanket in case you get cold. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.75,0:56:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.16,0:56:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不是個好爹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要踏入外面的世界了 而我卻什么都沒有教過你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you're heading into the big beyond and I haven't taught you a bloomin' thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.29,0:56:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 您當然教過我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. Hey. Sure you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.25,0:56:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情一定要上好雙保險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always quench your fire with water and earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.45,0:56:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在河流旁上廁所 免得到下游的時候想喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't squat by a river. Never know when you'll need a drink downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.62,0:56:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有禮貌的毛腳族才有可能更快地成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a Harfoot without manners is as like to get far in life as a square wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.91,0:56:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則寸步難行…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Square wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.04,0:56:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您說的這些我都認真聽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was listening to all of it, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.25,0:57:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探索河水能流多遠 去了解麻雀是在哪里學的春天之歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find where the river runs. Where the sparrows learn their songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.50,0:57:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.62,0:57:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我會多加小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.62,0:57:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.25,0:57:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會勇敢而無畏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.41,0:57:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, go on. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.79,0:57:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你還有這份勇氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on. Before you lose your nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.25,0:57:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說趁我們還有勇氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or we lose ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.25,0:58:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 諾瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait! Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.41,0:58:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.45,0:58:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我最愛的人總是要離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does everyone I love the most always have to go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.91,0:58:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不這樣做 我們就永遠學不到新東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I think if we didn't, then we'd never learn anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.25,0:58:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會回來嗎 你保證嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll come back? Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.00,0:58:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你保證會照顧好大家嗎  -當然了 蠢貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You promise to look after everyone? -Course I will, ankle-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.29,0:58:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我在這廣闊 而狂野的世界里最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're my best friend in this whole wide, wild world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.95,0:58:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意為你做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd do anything for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.37,0:59:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界沒那么大 波比 只不過是我們非常小而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The world's not that wide, Poppy. It's just that we're so bleedin' small.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.45,0:59:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緊那個高個子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stick close to that tall fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.00,0:59:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個患難與共的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a good friend in a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.08,0:59:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遠不及你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not so good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.95,0:59:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你確定嗎  -無比確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you certain? -More than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.00,0:59:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 他們都在向你揮手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, they're all waving at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.79,0:59:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我轉身 我就永遠都走不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I turn around, I won't ever be able to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.41,1:00:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那你在前邊帶頭可能會好一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then perhaps it would be best if you lead off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.50,1:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真到該走的時候 卻感覺腳如注鉛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, now that it comes to it, my feet feel heavy as iron.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.54,1:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說 我根本不知道前路在何方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention, I haven't an inkling which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.00,1:00:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.91,1:00:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.20,1:00:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.54,1:00:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊飄來的空氣有一股香甜味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a sweet smell on the air this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.08,1:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你懷疑的時候 埃拉諾白蘭地足…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When in doubt, Elanor Brandyfoot...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.62,1:00:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠跟著嗅覺走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}always follow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.12,1:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹蒼下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three rings for the Elven-kings
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.58,1:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈眾王得其三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.00,1:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石殿中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven for the Dwarf-lords
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.37,1:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人諸侯得其七\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In their halls of stone
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.66,1:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵世間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nine for Mortal Men
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.20,1:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死凡人得其九\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doomed to die
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.54,1:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多翳影 王座烏沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One for the Dark Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.87,1:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗魔君執其尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On his dark throne
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.16,1:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多翳影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the Land of Mordor
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.91,1:08:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪暗深處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.62,1:08:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪暗深處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.33,1:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統御余眾 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to rule them all
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.08,1:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網羅余眾 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to find them
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.08,1:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁錮余眾 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to bring them all
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.25,1:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁錮眾戒黑暗中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the darkness Bind them
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.25,1:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the Land of Mordor
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.41,1:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影幢幢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.16,1:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影幢幢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie...
